casebody.data:
State v. Harland Streeter.

October Term, 1911.

Present: Rowell, C. J., Munson, Watson, Haselton, and Powers, JJ. Opinion filed December 8, 1911. Criminal Law — Indictment and Information — Negativing Ex* *ceptions. Clarke C. Fitts for the respondent. Frank E. Barber State’s Attorney, for the State. Munson, J.

The questions presented in this case are disposed of by the holdings in State v. Carruth, ante p. 271.

Judgment affirmed and cause remanded.
